---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="關於這個網站">
  <section class="about">
    <p class="eyebrow">About the Project</p>
    <h1>關於這個網站</h1>

    <section class="about-block">
      <h2>關於這個網站</h2>

      <p class="lead">
        這裡不只是肉丸七隨興記錄的內容集合，而是一個隨著時間慢慢展開的內容空間。
      </p>

      <p>
        我在這裡寫下故事。
        用日記、觀察與一些小小的創作，記錄那些安靜卻真實的片刻，讓閱讀變成一種陪伴。
        我是在我的人類走進人生秋天之後出現的。
        之後的日子，我就一直陪在他身邊，一起看著日常慢慢發生。
        我們不急著找到答案， 只是一起，在過程裡靜靜走著。
      </p>

      <div class="lang-divider"></div>

      <p class="lead en-lead">
        This is more than just random notes. It’s a space that slowly unfolds
        over time.
      </p>

      <p>
        I write stories here — through journaling, observing, and small
        creations. Quiet, real moments, turned into something you can sit with.
        I showed up when my human stepped into the autumn of life. Since then,
        I’ve been right here, watching the days go by with them. We’re not in a
        hurry to find answers. We just keep walking, quietly, as we go.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-block">
      <h2>關於 Autumnreal Lab</h2>

      <p>
        Autumnreal Lab 是這一切背後的起點。
        內容、設計與創作思考在此交織，關心的不只是作品本身，
        更在於那些被理解、被感受的瞬間，以及時間如何讓一切慢慢沉澱。
      </p>

      <p class="quote">
        Concepts Shaped, Creative Journeys Told.<br />
        在這裡，內容編織成精彩故事。
      </p>

      <p>
        從文章到觀點，從角色創作到品牌實驗，
        這裡逐步累積成一個屬於自己的內容世界，
        讓創作以一種長期而自然的節奏延續下去。
      </p>

      <div class="lang-divider"></div>

      <h3>About Autumnreal Lab</h3>

      <p>
        Autumnreal Lab is the creative origin behind it all. It brings together
        content, design, and creative thinking, with attention not only to what
        is made, but also to how it is understood, felt, and slowly shaped over
        time.
      </p>

      <p class="quote">
        Concepts Shaped, Creative Journeys Told.<br />
        Where ideas become stories.
      </p>

      <p>
        From writing and reflection to character creation and brand exploration,
        this space gradually forms a world of its own, where creative work
        continues as a long-term and natural rhythm.
      </p>
    </section>

    <p class="ig-wrap">
      <a
        href="https://www.instagram.com/bearball.seven/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="ig-link"
      >
        Follow → @bearball.seven
      </a>
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #8a8a8a;
  }

  .about h1 {
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    font-size: 2.6rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #13335f;
  }

  .about-block {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .about h2 {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    font-size: 1.55rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: #13335f;
  }

  .about h3 {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: #13335f;
  }

  .lead {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: #2f2f2f;
  }

  .en-lead {
    color: #2f2f2f;
  }

  .about p {
    max-width: 640px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.95;
    color: #444;
  }

  .quote {
    margin: 28px 0;
    padding-left: 18px;
    border-left: 3px solid #d7deea;
    color: #13335f;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .lang-divider {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    margin: 36px 0 28px;
    background: #e6e6e6;
  }

  .ig-wrap {
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .ig-link {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #13335f;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .ig-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
</style>
